<b>Dojo</b><br><br><br>

The Makati Aikido Club dojo is located in a secure space well away from the street, and protected 24 hours a day by trained security staff. The training hall is a well-ventilated space with a 22-foot-high ceiling. The training mat is a rectangle of 90 square meters.<br><br><br>

